    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123540/extras/69b805fc639b0ec19786b9fae1816e54.avif?t=1681915263\" width=616 height=163 /></span><br><br>Guitar Zeros is a narrative deck builder where your goal is to help a DIY Punk band survive their road trip on the way to the Battle of The Bands.<br>Draw cards against story situations on the road with a unique system that mashes up deck building, narrative &amp; blackjack! Hit me baby one more time!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123540/extras/afda3d9f5eecec616ac599889b33dc5c.avif?t=1681915263\" width=616 height=163 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Improve Your Band &amp; Deck</strong></h2>As with any band just starting out, you’ve got your problems, and this is reflected in your deck at the beginning of the game…it sucks. Beat challenges to gain powerful new cards with various effects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story System</strong></h2>Your wins and losses are tracked to create the unique story of your band's tour.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Boss Battles of The Bands</strong></h2>Go up against rival bands, each with their own killer soundtrack and design.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123540/extras/d18e6dd56ad182726885434e10679317.avif?t=1681915263\" width=616 height=163 /></span>",
